{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AABgAzZm9RtpAvoF5xFVpE","type":"tool_result","content":"A CLI tool to do unsafe cluster and index manipulations on current node\n\nCommands\n--------\nrepurpose - Repurpose this node to another master/data role, cleaning up any excess persisted data\nunsafe-bootstrap - Forces the successful election of the current node after the permanent loss of the half or more master-eligible nodes\ndetach-cluster - Detaches this node from its cluster, allowing it to unsafely join a new cluster\noverride-version - Overwrite the version stored in this node's data path with [7.17.9] to bypass the version compatibility checks\nremove-settings - Removes persistent settings from the cluster state\nremove-customs - Removes custom metadata from the cluster state\n\nNon-option arguments:\ncommand              \n\nOption             Description        \n------             -----------        \n-E <KeyValuePair>  Configure a setting\n-h, --help         Show help          \n-s, --silent       Show minimal output\n-v, --verbose      Show verbose output","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"771fb90c-1f0e-4207-b44e-8e1f2b33f843","uuid":"5ef0211a-24c6-4603-b280-5e23912b2563","timestamp":"2026-06-26T04:38:29.930Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"A CLI tool to do unsafe cluster and index manipulations on current node\n\nCommands\n--------\nrepurpose - Repurpose this node to another master/data role, cleaning up any excess persisted data\nunsafe-bootstrap - Forces the successful election of the current node after the permanent loss of the half or more master-eligible nodes\ndetach-cluster - Detaches this node from its cluster, allowing it to unsafely join a new cluster\noverride-version - Overwrite the version stored in this node's data path with [7.17.9] to bypass the version compatibility checks\nremove-settings - Removes persistent settings from the cluster state\nremove-customs - Removes custom metadata from the cluster state\n\nNon-option arguments:\ncommand              \n\nOption             Description        \n------             -----------        \n-E <KeyValuePair>  Configure a setting\n-h, --help         Show help          \n-s, --silent       Show minimal output\n-v, --verbose      Show verbose output","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
